Package src.model

Class ReplenishRequest

Object
ReplenishRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ReplenishRequest extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a replenishment request made by a pharmacist to request additional medication. Contains details about the request, such as the pharmacist's ID, request ID, medication details, and request status.

2024-11-13

  • Constructor Details

    • ReplenishRequest

      public ReplenishRequest(String pharmacistID, String requestID, String medicationName, int medicationAmount)
      Constructs a new ReplenishRequest with the specified pharmacist ID, request ID, medication name, and medication amount. The medication ID is fetched from the database, and the request status is set to PENDING by default.
      Parameters:
      pharmacistID - The ID of the pharmacist making the request.
      requestID - The unique ID for the replenishment request.
      medicationName - The name of the medication requested for replenishment.
      medicationAmount - The amount of medication requested for replenishment.
